entries.title: Survivor found 'gasping for life' among bodies dumped on Zambian roadside
entries.description: Zambia's police service says it is investigating the deaths of 27 men, all believed to be Ethiopian nationals, whose bodies were found on Sunday "dumped" by the roadside near the capital, Lusaka.

entries.title: Kosovo calls for NATO intervention after weekend of violence amid rising ethnic tensions
entries.description: Kosovo's Prime Minister urged NATO peacekeeping troops to intervene after minority Serb protesters blocked roads and unknown gunmen exchanged fire with police over the weekend amid rising ethnic tensions in the country's restive north.

entries.title: China to abolish its Covid-19 trace tracking service, the 'Mobile Itinerary card,' on Tuesday, officials say
entries.description: China will abolish its Covid-19 trace tracking service, the "Mobile Itinerary card," on Tuesday, officials say.
